    "causal_summary": "Replace the hardcoded embeddinggemma-300m default with a smart precedence-chain auto-selection at bootstrap. Probe environment in order — Voyage API key → OpenAI API key → Ollama daemon+jina-v3 → hf-local — and persist the choice to vec_metadata. Purge all llama-cpp / embeddinggemma in-process loader code (Metal GGUF, node-llama-cpp deps, the 750 MB legacy DB), replacing the legacy fallback path. Ollama becomes the always-available local fallback when cloud APIs aren't configured.",
